	This is my One Piece OC set in an alternate universe, as such many things will be different from the Cannon Lore.<br><br>

<details open="open"><summary class="section-head">Appearance</summary>

	Sparrow D. Alys boasts long, wavy dark blue hair that flows elegantly over her shoulders and down her back, with a few strands artfully braided near the crown. Her light skin, dusted with freckles, adds to her youthful charm. Alys typically dons a white off-shoulder ribbed sweater that highlights her shoulders, paired with fitted, muted olive green pants held in place by a black belt featuring golden accents. Alternatively, she may wear a sleek dark long-sleeved top with slightly sheer sleeves, complemented by high-waisted, form-fitting black pants and a minimalist black belt. Alys is always seen with her katana, Shodai Kitetsu, never far from her side.
	

</details><br>

